<html>
<head>
<META NAME="ROBOTS" CONTENT="NOINDEX, NOFOLLOW">
<META NAME="ROBOTS" CONTENT="NOARCHIVE">
<title>Outgoing Mail Server</title>

<!----lightbox-->
<script type="text/javascript" src="/zz/fancybox/jquery-latest.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/zz/fancybox/jquery.fancybox.js?v=2.1.5"></script>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/zz/fancybox/jquery.fancybox.css?v=2.1.5" media="screen" />
<!---lightbox--->

<SCRIPT LANGUAGE="JAVASCRIPT">

jQuery( document ).ready(function( $ ) {
	$('.fancybox').fancybox({
		fitToView	: false,
		maxWidth	: 700,
		maxHeight	: 450,
		autoSize	: false,
		openEffect	: 'none',
		closeEffect	: 'none'
	});
});


function SmtpAccSave(par) 
      { 
       document.theForm.action="/wc.dll?mpmainten~SmtpAccSave~<%=pcSCR%>~"+par;
       document.theForm.submit();
      }

function SmtpAccTest(par) { 
  var frm=document.theForm;
//  alert(par)
     { 
    window.open('/wc.dll?mpmainten~SmtpAccTest~<%=pcSCR%>~'+par+'~'+frm.MAILTO.value,'EANITHING','toolbar=no,location=no,directories=no,status=no,menubar=no,resizable=no,copyhistory=no,scrollbars=yes,width=500,height=350');
    self.name="main"
     }
}

function CopyMe(TextToCopy) {
  var TempText = document.createElement("input");
  TempText.value = TextToCopy;
  document.body.appendChild(TempText);
  TempText.select();
  
  document.execCommand("copy");
  document.body.removeChild(TempText);
  
  alert("SPF Record copied: " + TempText.value);
}

</SCRIPT>

<STYLE TYPE="text/css">
	 .button	{	font-size: 9pt;
					font-weight: bold;
  				  	font-family: Arial;
                    width: 50; 
                    height: 25; 
                    cursor: pointer;}
	 .addnew	{	font-size: 9pt;
					font-weight: bold;
  				  	font-family: Arial;
                    width: 70; 
                    height: 25; 
                    cursor: pointer;}
                    
</style>
</head>
<body BGCOLOR="#4E6699">
<div align="center">
  <center>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="950">
  <tr>
    <td width="100%" align="center" height="25" background="/ZZ/images/bar-green.gif">
    <a href="javascript:window.close()"><img border="0" src="/zz/images/x-yellow.gif" align="right" width="17" height="18"></a><b><font face="Verdana" color="#FFFFFF">Outgoing Mail Server</font></b></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="100%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<br>     
<table border="0" align="center" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="60%">
  <tr>
    <td align="right"><img border="0" src="/zz/images/alert.jpg" width="30" height="30"></td>  
    <td align="left"><a href="wc.dll?mpmainten~emailserrorlog~<%=pcSCR%>" style="color:blue;" target="_blank"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="red"><b>Outgoing Emails Error Report</b></font></a></td>
 </tr>
</table>
<br>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="100%" height="5">
  <tr>
    <td width="100%" align="center" height="83">	
 <form name="theForm" method="POST">    			
<table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#C0C0C0" width="98%">
  <tr>
    <td width="3%" align="center" bgcolor="#008000">&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="18%" align="center" bgcolor="#008000"><b><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Outgoing Mail Server</font></b></td>
    <td width="25%" align="center" bgcolor="#008000"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="#FFFFFF" ><b>Email Address</b></font></td>
    <td width="14%" align="center" bgcolor="#008000"><b><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Email Password</font></b></td>
    <td width="6%" align="center" bgcolor="#008000"><b><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Active</font></b></td>
    <td width="8%" align="center" bgcolor="#008000"><b><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Test It</font></b></td>
    <td width="4%" align="center" bgcolor="#008000"><b><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Del</font></b></td>
    <td width="5%" align="center">&nbsp;</td>
 </tr>
 <%SELECT _SMTPACC 
 SCAN %>
  <tr style="line-height:30px;">
    <td width="3%" align="center"><font style="font-family:Verdana;font-size:9pt;"><%=ALLT(STR(RECNO()))%></font>&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="18%">&nbsp;<font face="Verdana" size="2"><%=ALLT(PROVNAME)%></font></td>
    <td width="25%" align="left"><input type="text" autocomplete="off" name="<%='E'+ALLT(STR(SMTPACCID,8)) %>" size="30" value="<%=ALLT(ACCTEMAIL)%>" tabindex="2"></td>
    <td width="14%" align="center"><input type="text" autocomplete="off" name="<%='P'+ALLT(STR(SMTPACCID,8)) %>" size="11" value="<%=ALLT(XPASS)%>" style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;" onclick='this.value=""' onFocus='this.value=""' tabindex="3"></td>		
    <td width="6%" align="center"><input type="checkbox" name="<%='A'+ALLT(STR(SMTPACCID,8))%>" value="ON" <%=IIF(ACTIVE,'checked','')%> tabindex="6"></td>
	<td width="8%" align="center"><% IF SMTPID > 200 %><a href="javascript:SmtpAccTest(<%=ALLT(STR(SMTPACCID,8))%>)"><font style="font-family:Verdana;font-size:10pt;">Test Email</font></a><%ENDIF%></td>	
	<td width="4%" align="center"><% IF SMTPID > 200 %><input type="checkbox" name="<%='D'+ALLT(STR(SMTPACCID,8))%>" value="ON" tabindex="7"><%ENDIF%></td>	
	<td width="5%"><input type="button" value="Save" name="B1" onclick="SmtpAccSave(<%=ALLT(STR(SMTPACCID,8))%>)" class="button"></td>	
  </tr>
<% ENDSCAN %>
  <tr>
    <td align="center" colspan="8"><hr color="#C0C0C0" width="99%" size="1"></hr></td>
 </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="21%" align="center" colspan="2">
    <select size="1" name="S1">
		<option selected>< Select Provider ></option>
		 <%	SELECT _SP
		    SCAN %>		      
		<option value="<%=ALLT(STR(SMTPID))%>"><%=ALLT(SMTPNAME)%></option>
		 <% ENDSCAN %>
		</select></td>
    <td width="25%" align="left"><input type="text" autocomplete="off" name="E1" size="30" value=""></td>
    <td width="14%" align="center"><input type="text" autocomplete="off" name="P1" size="11" value="" style="font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;" onclick='this.value=""' onFocus='this.value=""'></td> 
    <td width="6%" align="center"><input type="checkbox" name="A1" value="ON" tabindex="6"></td>
	<td width="17%" colspan="3"><input type="button" value="Add New" name="B1" onclick="SmtpAccSave(1)" class="addnew"></td>	
 </tr>
</table>
 <br>
<table border="0" align="center" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="98%">
  <tr>
    <td width="52%">&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="48%"><b><font color="#008000" face="Arial" size="2">Send test email to:</font></b>    
    <input type="text" name="MAILTO" value="<%=pcMAILTO %>" size="30" tabindex="2"></td>
 </tr>
</table>   			
 </form>        
<table border="1" cellspacing="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#C0C0C0" width="98%">
  <tr>
    <td width="81%" style="line-height:27px;"><font face="Verdana" size="2">
    <b>Important!!! Please Read Instructions &amp; Recommendations:</b><br>
    1. Add SPF TXT Record to your domain DNS to validate your domain as an email sender.<br>v=spf1 ip4:208.68.236.200 ~all
    &nbsp;<input type="button" style="font-size:9pt;font-weight:bold;font-family:Arial;width:115;height:25;cursor:pointer;" onclick="CopyMe('v=spf1 ip4:208.68.236.200 ~all')" value="Copy SPF Record"><br>
    <b>Coming Soon:</b> Add <b>DKIM</b> to get seal of email approval.
    <hr></hr>
    2. Do not  activate an outgoing email  if you're unsure about the outgoing email setting.<br>    
    3. It's recommended to integrate email(s) account(s) provided by your  <b>Emails Hosting Company</b>.<br>
    4. Test your email integration by sending an email from an <b>Estimate</b>.<br>
    * Test Email  confirms that the email and password match.
    <hr></hr>
    <b>Gmail Business (GSuite):</b> <a href="https://www.gmail.com" target="_blank">www.gmail.com</a><br>
    Outgoing Mail Server: <b>smtp.gmail.com</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Port: <b>587</b><br>
    <b>Requires turning on <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/security/lesssecureapps">"Less Secure Apps"</a>.</b> Move the toggle to <b>TURN ON.</b><br>
    <hr></hr>
    <b>Microsoft Office 365</b>: <a href="https://login.microsoftonline.com" target="_blank">login.microsoftonline.com</a><br>
    Outgoing Mail Server: <b>smtp.office365.com</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Port: <b>587</b><br>
    <b>Requires Enabling SMTP Client Authentication for each email.</b><br>More 
    details available here: <a class="fancybox fancybox.iframe" href="/zz/help/office365.htm">How To Enable SMTP Client Authentication</a> 
    or call Go Daddy support and ask to enable it for all emails.<br>
    <hr></hr>
    </hr>
    Integration availability is upon your agreement with your <b>Emails Hosting Company</b>.</font></td>
    <td width="19%" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="2"><b>Outgoing email integration MAY NOT be compatible 
    with:</b><br><br><b>1. Gmail (@gmail.com)<br>2. BlueHost.com<br>3. Host Monster<br>4. Host Gator</b><br>5. Yahoo (@Yahoo.com)<br>6. Register.com<br>7. Optimum.com (A.K.A optonline)<br>
    8. verizon.com/net<br>9. Road Runner<br>10. Hotmail/MSN<br>11. AOL</font></td>
 </tr>
</table>
   &nbsp;</td>
  </tr>
</table>
   </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="100%" height="25" background="/zz/images/bgdown.gif"><font color="#FFFFFF" size="2" face="Arial"><%=pcUSER%>&nbsp;-<%=pcCOMPANY%></font></td>
  </tr>
</table>
  </center>
</div>
</body>
</html>